            <title>[HBASE-2264] Adjust the contrib apps to the Maven project layout</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2264</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is a follow-up patch for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2254&quot; title=&quot;Improvements to the Maven POMs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-2254&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-2254&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This patch aims only at the contrib apps to change their layout to the standard Maven project layout.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
